  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 90fb537b6042fd55be7899ba5c939f45, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  _englishVersion: 'Creating game servers directly from the game is no longer supported.

    There
    are currently 3 ways of creating a SCP:SL server:

    - You can download SCP:SL
    dedicated server (Steam AppID: 996560) and run it on your computer

    - You
    can rent a VPS or a Dedicated Server from a hosting provider and run SCP:SL dedicated
    server there

    - You can rent a SCP:SL server from a game hosting provider
    that supports SCP:SL (eg. ZAP Hosting)



    Click the links below to get more
    info.

    You can ask our tech support (link to our Discord server can be found
    in the main menu) for assistance.'
  _fileId: 2
  _line: 81
